title: The Returned S1 Ep6 - Lucy
description:
The Returned S1 Ep6 - Lucy

Lucy - There's an electricity outage throughout the town. Pierre forms a community around Camille, who is now seen as a kind of 'prophet'. After being 'killed' by Thomas, Simon comes back to life again and takes off with the enigmatic Lucy. Julie finds refuge at Laure's house with Victor, whose body seems to be becoming strangely distorted. Lena grows closer to Serge but has to escape back to the town. 

From France, in French
